The study aims to explore patients perception of chronic abdominal pain after Roux en Y gastric bypass surgery for morbid obesity.

 The investigators aim to describe characteristics of symptoms of pain.

 Potential risk factors for developing abdominal pain post gastric bypass will be explored.

